title: Prince Harry hears how a patient chased a paramedic who 'wanted to kill her'
text:
Prince Harry hears how a patient chased a paramedic who 'wanted to kill her'  23 GMT 
Prince Harry has heard a paramedic describe how she was chased by a patient who threatened to kill her. 
He was visiting the London Ambulance Service as part of Time to Talk Day - an annual awareness day run by Time to Change aimed at getting the nation talking about mental health. Read more
